Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.75,0:01:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道劍心在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.92,0:01:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.69,0:01:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人是不是劍心說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.09,0:01:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在東京認識的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.33,0:02:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十一話\N尋找恩師比古清十郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.17,0:02:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.47,0:02:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心真的在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.61,0:02:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他前腳走我們後腳就到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.89,0:02:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來緋村在東京還有朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.99,0:02:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就知道緋村的來歷不簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.60,0:02:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想見他一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你先回答我一個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.37,0:02:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該知道\N緋村來京都的目的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.11,0:02:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.28,0:02:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你就這樣\N隨便跑去找緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.75,0:02:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對他是很危險的事  你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是想見緋村嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果換成是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.83,0:03:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千里迢迢從東京\N到這來找一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.24,0:03:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認為會隨便的\N做出不該做的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.51,0:03:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天涯海角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.35,0:03:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都會去找你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.12,0:03:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.36,0:03:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就帶你們去找劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.10,0:03:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快告訴我緋村住在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問到了 小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.54,0:03:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.61,0:03:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帶你們去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.18,0:04:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這樣子對一介的陶藝家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是很不禮貌的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.72,0:04:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比古清十郎不是陶藝家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.73,0:04:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久沒這樣了  老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.51,0:05:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.98,0:05:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心情不好  不想見客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.15,0:05:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了  我把小姑娘叫回去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.98,0:05:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.48,0:05:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是心情不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.42,0:05:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在很好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.46,0:05:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是個老不修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.83,0:05:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人叫我拿這個給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.46,0:05:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了  是誰交給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.10,0:05:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身材高大聲音宏亮的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.29,0:05:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.13,0:05:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我應該先向你磕頭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.90,0:06:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿操很想見你一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.54,0:06:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為不想帶給阿操麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.14,0:06:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盟主只留下這麼一個愛孫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.34,0:06:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都不願意  見到她有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.48,0:06:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你找我有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在找個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.35,0:06:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫緋村劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.59,0:06:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.43,0:06:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.50,0:06:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫夠了 你該覺醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.37,0:06:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在需要的是心靈的靜養
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.31,0:06:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然你也是御庭幫的成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.11,0:06:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你從不瞭解我的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.12,0:06:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再最後告訴你一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.19,0:06:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你非要\N讓御庭屋的面子丟光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.36,0:07:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就先把我給殺了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.43,0:07:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會不惜一切把你擊垮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這麼巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.97,0:07:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到你也到京都來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.90,0:07:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別裝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.74,0:07:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰一路跟著我來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.01,0:07:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.27,0:07:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是今天早上才到京都的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.14,0:07:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真是奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.35,0:07:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是今天早上剛到京都的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.28,0:07:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裝不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.42,0:08:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我向你道歉就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.79,0:08:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不一起來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.23,0:08:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要回志志雄的住處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.70,0:08:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫我去我就去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.64,0:08:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是要打聽緋村的住處嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.58,0:08:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可以互相交換情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.75,0:08:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧  你帶我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經十五年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.89,0:08:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間過得可真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.99,0:08:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你找我比古清十郎有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你要改頭換姓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.30,0:08:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以陶藝家的身份隱居起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.47,0:08:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰叫我不是阿諛奉承的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.47,0:08:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與其和一些貪官污吏\N同流合污
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.01,0:08:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒不如做個藝術家\N來得自在一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是老樣子  一點都沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別轉移話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.75,0:09:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底找我有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是你的老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.89,0:09:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不說我也知道你在想什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就明講了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.53,0:09:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十五年前\N你沒教我的飛天御劍流精髓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.34,0:09:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望老師能教我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.88,0:09:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.91,0:09:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候就是隨便收留了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.05,0:09:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才造成了今天的你\N現在我怎麼能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.42,0:09:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.66,0:09:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來你今天是有備而來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.53,0:09:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心的老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.87,0:10:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比古清十郎是唯一\N貫通飛天御劍流的武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.14,0:10:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的武功無人能比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.65,0:10:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然還有劍心不會的武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.48,0:10:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心一定是去\N找比古教他武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼劍心武功就更高強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.22,0:10:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就沒人打得過劍心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.92,0:10:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.27,0:10:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於可以見到劍心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.58,0:10:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是為了志志雄那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.05,0:10:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想再重回殺手的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.06,0:10:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請您教我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.63,0:10:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍是兇器  劍術是殺人術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.70,0:11:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是改變不了的事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.17,0:11:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己的理想和現實的危難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.21,0:11:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何者重要  你已想清楚了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.91,0:11:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十五年前我就錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.29,0:11:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.09,0:11:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個笨蛋\N你以為出去能幫助你修行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.10,0:11:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這個動亂的時代\N我不能再坐視不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.80,0:11:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我學飛天御劍流\N就是要保護弱小的老百姓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你實現了你的理想了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.71,0:11:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自大的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.41,0:11:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.61,0:11:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.78,0:11:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先把我打倒了再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.92,0:11:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還來真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你自己說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真拿你沒轍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.73,0:12:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流如果練不好的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會走火入魔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.57,0:12:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.37,0:12:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只知道現在最重要的是\N要解救那些可憐的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.21,0:12:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的脾氣和小時候\N一點都沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.42,0:12:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還記得你的這個傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.82,0:12:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是怎麼來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.86,0:12:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你十四歲的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.46,0:12:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍法就超越常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.53,0:12:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你的思想並未\N如你的劍術一樣成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你年輕時血氣方剛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.53,0:12:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才留下這個褪不去的傷疤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.04,0:12:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心裏還在為\N殺人與不殺人矛盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.77,0:12:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼練得成飛天御劍術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.41,0:12:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又怎麼打得過志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.45,0:13:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算飛天御劍流\N能夠解救苦難的人民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.99,0:13:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但劍是自由是\N是不屬於任何權利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.20,0:13:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是不明白這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.73,0:13:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你根本沒有資格\N學飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.37,0:13:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這裏沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.35,0:13:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.82,0:13:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.05,0:13:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.46,0:13:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.66,0:13:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村就在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.96,0:13:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.40,0:13:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這種笨蛋\N我根本不該教你武功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.07,0:13:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說誰笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.81,0:13:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.11,0:13:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿操  彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.26,0:14:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.13,0:14:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們認識嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.23,0:14:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到今天來了那麼多客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.31,0:14:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心  你去提水來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.94,0:14:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要我提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫你提你就去提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我不在\N老師還不是自己要提
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.85,0:14:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是這麼沒大沒小\N還不快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.86,0:14:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.93,0:14:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.41,0:15:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在發什麼呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.18,0:15:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易見到面了\N怎麼不講話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間寶貴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.69,0:15:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人就是劍心的老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.16,0:15:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就是飛天御劍術的繼承者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.20,0:15:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你今年幾歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.77,0:15:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四十三歲  怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.38,0:15:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個樣子像四十三歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心已經二十八歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.68,0:15:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二十八歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.68,0:15:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.58,0:15:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是練飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.32,0:15:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才變成這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.06,0:15:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們來到底有什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.46,0:15:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是來找劍心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.66,0:15:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.90,0:16:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,見面以後呢\N不是要一起回東京嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.97,0:16:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就坦白說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.24,0:16:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是一起戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.14,0:16:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只不過想再見他一面而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.55,0:16:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到我的笨徒弟\N還這麼有人緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.99,0:16:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心的事\N你好像什麼都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.83,0:16:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊  你們願意告訴我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.03,0:16:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我教那個木頭人\N飛天御劍流的劍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.40,0:16:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經十年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.17,0:16:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這晚唯一記得的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.97,0:16:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要他告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.11,0:16:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你們告訴我他的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰和彌彥都來京都了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.08,0:16:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼左之助不久後也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.62,0:17:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和志志雄決鬥的事就更困難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宗次郎回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.02,0:17:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見了  焰靈秘劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.39,0:17:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這次帶來什麼好東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.36,0:17:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帶來東日本的十本刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.60,0:17:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見了安慈\N你的修行完成了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.10,0:17:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蝙也  你的傷怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.01,0:17:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.51,0:17:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夷腕坊你還是老樣子\N一點都沒變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.85,0:17:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.38,0:18:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有稀客來訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.33,0:18:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這十年都在全國各地流浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.77,0:18:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幫助需要幫助的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.84,0:18:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次回來\N只為專程學習飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.51,0:18:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是為了償還\N那些被你殺死的人命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.18,0:18:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩者都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.18,0:18:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我無法解救\N那些苦命人的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.79,0:18:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的脾氣還是和以前一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.33,0:18:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就教你\N飛天御劍流最後的精髓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.67,0:18:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定要打敗志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.04,0:18:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你打不倒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.41,0:18:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就枉費我一番苦心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.18,0:19:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.48,0:19:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.79,0:19:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來京都  你生氣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.76,0:19:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一半心在志志雄身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.80,0:19:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.47,0:19:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄藏身的地方還不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.12,0:19:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心  你從不願回頭看我一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.60,0:19:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先說在前頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使你學會\N飛天御劍流的最後部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.87,0:20:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不必高興得太早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.50,0:20:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為你將會背負\N守護這個時代的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.65,0:20:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個責任是很重大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.82,0:20:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一個人的幸福\N也掌握在你手裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那個來京都找你的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.39,0:20:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你犧牲了\N對她將是不幸的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.40,0:20:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千萬記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.27,0:20:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論你有多強  你都只是個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.74,0:20:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是神僊或菩薩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.47,0:20:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.28,0:20:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.75,0:20:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們為什麼\N一定要這麼晚回去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.25,0:20:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心要開始練功了\N我們不能打擾他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.26,0:20:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.76,0:20:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經達成見劍心的願望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.43,0:21:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你們不嫌棄\N就到我家來住吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.94,0:21:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.24,0:21:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流的精髓\N到底是什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.14,0:21:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是最厲害的武功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.78,0:21:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最厲害的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.52,0:21:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然想到有件事\N忘了告訴劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.52,0:21:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了  是蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.49,0:21:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.63,0:21:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四乃森蒼紫\N已經來京都要暗殺劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.56,0:21:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要讓劍心知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.53,0:21:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.90,0:21:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.04,0:21:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.34,0:21:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們說的是真的嗎\N蒼紫來京都了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.01,0:21:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.55,0:21:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彌彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.68,0:21:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰  他是御庭幫的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.75,0:21:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你接近劍心有什麼目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.56,0:21:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是蒼紫要你做的\N你是不是來報仇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.79,0:22:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.13,0:22:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫和緋村到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.10,0:22:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭幫的人究竟怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.24,0:22:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這騙子  別再演戲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.51,0:22:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個夠了沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.51,0:22:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰  他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.24,0:22:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是阿操\N我們怎麼會找得到劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.85,0:22:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰  你也知道蒼紫的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.22,0:22:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.42,0:22:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託
